{"tha-ap463:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap463:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap463:0.3":"Salakusumiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap463:1.1":"“Parinibbute bhagavati, ","tha-ap463:1.2":"jalajuttamanamake; ","tha-ap463:1.3":"Aropitamhi citake, ","tha-ap463:1.4":"salapupphamapujayim. ","tha-ap463:2.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap463:2.2":"Yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap463:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap463:2.4":"Citapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap463:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap463:3.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap463:3.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap463:3.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap463:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap463:4.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap463:4.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap463:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap463:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap463:5.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap463:5.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap463:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap463:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma salakusumiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap463:7.1":"Salakusumiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}